Package com.intellij.util.xml

Class ResolvingConverter<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.util.xml.Converter<T>
      • com.intellij.util.xml.ResolvingConverter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResolvingHint
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractMemberResolveConverter, AbstractMethodResolveConverter, BooleanValueConverter, DelimitedListConverter, DomResolveConverter, EnumConverter, NumberValueConverter, QuotedValueConverter, ResolvingConverter.StringConverter, ResolvingConverter.WrappedResolvingConverter

    public abstract class ResolvingConverter<T>
extends Converter<T>
implements ResolvingHint
    If converter extends this class, the corresponding XML PsiReference will take completion variants from getVariants(ConvertContext) method.
